      @Nonnull public <T> FunctionField<T> getCopyWithCopyField(FunctionField<T> template)
      Get the field that stores a redudant copy of a parent item's value at the relation item, to enforce a CopyConstraint added with copyWith(FunctionField).
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if the field given as parameter does not belong to this SetField's type.
